						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							A single termite is weak, fragile and usually needs to stay moist to survive. Their creature power is in numbers. Some termite nests can house millions of termites! They all work together to find food, clean the nest, rebuild, fortify and protect their home.
						</text>
