					Danger Alert
				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							Termites are prey for many creatures such as ants, aardvarks, anteaters, sloth bears, pangolins, and bat eared foxes. They can also be eaten by spiders, and nematode worms.
						</text>
