			</contentSection><contentSection id="5">
				<title>
					Livin' Creature Style
				</title>
				<navigationLabel>
					Livin' Termite Style!
				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							There are different kinds of termites in every population. Worker termites look for food, store food, and maintain the nest. Soldier termites are strong, have big jaws, and special armor, which are useful when under attack. Some termite soldiers can even produce a stinky chemical to deter predators. King and queen termites have wings and help establish new colonies.
						</text>
